Chapter 8: Conclusion and Algorithmic Readiness

8.1 Summary of Contributions

This thesis has developed a complete mathematical framework for the certification of non‑thermal plasma‑catalytic VOC oxidation under Martian low‑pressure conditions. The key contributions are:

1. A certified reduced‑order model (Chapter 2) for 35‑species plasma chemistry at 600 Pa, including a Knudsen‑regime correction with O(\mathrm{Kn}_e) error bound. We proved global existence and uniqueness of solutions (Theorem 2.1) and derived a POD‑based ROM with a 5% error certificate (Theorem 2.2).
