4. Bayesian optimization under stochastic constraints (Chapter 5) using the SAFE‑BO algorithm. We proved convergence of simple regret at rate O(\sqrt{\gamma_T/T}) (Theorem 5.1) and incorporated multi‑fidelity for lifetime certification.
