· The RL controller is tested in simulation with the ROM (ARL 4‑5).
· The BO is tested on test functions and on the ROM (ARL 4).
· The CV system is tested on synthetic scalograms (ARL 4).

All components are integrated into a single software suite, ready for deployment on hardware (e.g., JPL/ESTEC testbeds) to achieve ARL 6.

